<text><body>
<lb n="0710a07" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0710a08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0710a09" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1022A [No. 1023]</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0710a10" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><note n="0710001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第十八帖，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note><cb:jhead>一切如來心祕密全身舍利寶篋
<lb n="0710a11" ed="T"/>印陀羅尼經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0710a12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0710a13" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0710002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔開府…號〕三十字－【三】，（開府…號）三十字＝（特進試鴻臚卿）六字【甲】</note><note n="0710002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…號）三十字【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->（開府…號）三十字＝（特進試鴻臚卿）六字【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="30" n="0710002"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅
<lb n="0710a14" ed="T"/>國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空謚
<lb n="0710a15" ed="T"/>大鑒正號</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">特進試鴻臚卿</rdg></app><note n="0710003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門＝大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智【宋】【元】【甲】，唐三藏沙門大廣智【明】【乙】</note><note n="0710003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門【大】，大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智【宋】【元】【甲】，唐三藏沙門大廣智【明】【乙】</note><app n="0710003"><lem wit="【大】">大廣智大興善寺三
<lb n="0710a16" ed="T"/>藏沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】">唐三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>不空<note n="0710004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔奉詔〕－【明】【乙】</note><note n="0710004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉詔【大】，〔－〕【明】【乙】</note><app n="0710004"><lem wit="【大】">奉　詔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0710a17" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT19p0710a1701">如是我聞。一時薄伽梵在摩伽陀國無垢園
<lb n="0710a18" ed="T"/>寶光明池中。與大菩薩眾。及大聲聞僧。天龍
<lb n="0710a19" ed="T"/>藥叉健闥婆阿蘇羅迦樓羅緊那羅摩睺羅伽
<lb n="0710a20" ed="T"/>人非人等。無量百千眾俱前後圍繞。</p>
<lb n="0710a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0710a2101">爾時眾中有一大婆羅門。名無垢妙光。多聞
<lb n="0710a22" ed="T"/>聰慧人所樂見。常奉十善。於三寶所決定信
<lb n="0710a23" ed="T"/>向。善心慇重智慧微細。<note n="0710005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">常＋（恒）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常【大】，常恒【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710005"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">常恒</rdg></app>欲令一切眾生
<lb n="0710a24" ed="T"/><note n="0710006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">相應＝圓滿ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相應【大】，圓滿【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710006"><lem wit="【大】">相應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">圓滿</rdg></app>善利。大富豐饒資具圓滿。時彼婆羅門
<lb n="0710a25" ed="T"/>無垢妙光。從座而起往詣佛所。遶佛七匝。以
<lb n="0710a26" ed="T"/>眾香花奉獻世尊。無價妙衣瓔珞珠鬘持覆
<lb n="0710a27" ed="T"/>佛上。頂禮雙足却住一面。作是請言。<note n="0710007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯＝惟【三】【乙】＊</note><note n="0710007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯【大】＊，惟【宋】【元】【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0710007"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">惟</rdg></app>願
<lb n="0710a28" ed="T"/>世尊與諸大眾。明日晨朝至我宅中受我供
<lb n="0710a29" ed="T"/>養。</p>
<pb n="0710b" xml:id="T19.1022A.0710b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0710b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0710b0101">爾時世尊默然許之。時婆羅門知佛受請。遽
<lb n="0710b02" ed="T"/>還所住。即於是夜廣辦餚饍百味飲食。張施
<lb n="0710b03" ed="T"/>殿宇種種莊嚴。至明旦已與諸眷屬。持眾香
<lb n="0710b04" ed="T"/>花及諸伎樂。至如來所白言。時至願赴我請。
<lb n="0710b05" ed="T"/>今正是時。願垂聽許。</p>
<lb n="0710b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0710b0601">爾時世<note n="0710008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尊＋（軟語）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尊【大】，尊軟語【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710008"><lem wit="【大】">尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">尊軟語</rdg></app>安慰彼婆羅門無垢妙<note n="0710009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光＋（言）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0710009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光【大】，光言【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0710009"><lem wit="【大】">光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">光言</rdg></app><note n="0710010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔已〕ィ－【乙】</note><note n="0710010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已【大】，〔－〕【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710010"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>顧
<lb n="0710b07" ed="T"/>視大眾告言。汝等皆應往彼婆羅門家。為欲
<lb n="0710b08" ed="T"/>令彼獲大利故。於時世尊即從座起。纔起座
<lb n="0710b09" ed="T"/>已。從佛身出種種光明。間錯妙色照觸十方。
<lb n="0710b10" ed="T"/>悉皆警覺<note n="0710011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一切如來既警覺〕－【甲】</note><note n="0710011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一切如來既警覺【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0710011"><lem wit="【大】">一切。如來既警覺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>已。然後取道。
<lb n="0710b11" ed="T"/>時婆羅門以恭敬心。持<note n="0710012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妙＝以【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0710012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙【大】，以【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0710012"><lem wit="【大】">妙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">以</rdg></app>香花與諸眷屬及
<lb n="0710b12" ed="T"/>天龍八部釋梵護世。先行治道奉引如來。爾
<lb n="0710b13" ed="T"/>時世尊前路不遠。中<note n="0710013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">止＝至【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0710013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">止【大】，至【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0710013"><lem wit="【大】">止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">至</rdg></app>一園名曰豐財。於彼
<lb n="0710b14" ed="T"/>園中有古朽塔。摧壞崩倒荊棘所沒。榛草充
<lb n="0710b15" ed="T"/>遍覆諸礓礫。狀若土堆。</p>
<lb n="0710b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0710b1601">爾時世尊徑往塔<note n="0710014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">所＋（于）【乙】</note><note n="0710014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所【大】，所于【乙】</note><app n="0710014"><lem wit="【大】">所</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">所于</rdg></app>。時<note n="0710015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔朽〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0710015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">朽【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0710015"><lem wit="【大】">朽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>塔上放大光明
<lb n="0710b17" ed="T"/>赫然熾盛。於土聚中出<note n="0710016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔善哉〕ィ－【乙】</note><note n="0710016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善哉【大】，〔－〕【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710016"><lem wit="【大】">善哉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>聲讚言善哉善
<lb n="0710b18" ed="T"/>哉釋迦牟尼如來今日所行極善境界。又言。
<lb n="0710b19" ed="T"/>汝婆羅門。汝於今日獲大善利。爾時世尊禮
<lb n="0710b20" ed="T"/>彼朽塔右遶三匝。脫身上衣用覆其上。泫然
<lb n="0710b21" ed="T"/>垂淚涕<note n="0710017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">泗＝血【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0710017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泗【大】，血【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0710017"><lem wit="【大】">泗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">血</rdg></app>交流。泣已微笑。當爾之時。十方
<lb n="0710b22" ed="T"/>諸佛皆同觀視亦皆<note n="0710018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">泣＝流ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泣【大】，流【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710018"><lem wit="【大】">泣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">流</rdg></app>淚。俱放光明來照是
<lb n="0710b23" ed="T"/>塔。是時大眾集會。皆同怪異。驚怖而住。爾時
<lb n="0710b24" ed="T"/>金剛手菩薩亦皆流淚。威焰熾盛執杵旋轉。
<lb n="0710b25" ed="T"/>往詣佛所白言。世尊此何因緣現是光相。何
<lb n="0710b26" ed="T"/><note n="0710019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔故〕－【三】【甲】，〔故於〕ィ－【乙】</note><note n="0710019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故於【大】，〔－〕【校異-乙】，於【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0710019"><lem wit="【大】">故於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">於</rdg></app>如來眼流淚如是。此是佛之大瑞光相
<lb n="0710b27" ed="T"/>現前。<app type="star" corresp="#0710007"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">惟</rdg></app>願如來於此大眾。解釋我疑。時薄
<lb n="0710b28" ed="T"/>伽梵告金剛手。此大全身舍<note n="0710020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＋（積）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利【大】，利積【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710020"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">利積</rdg></app>聚如<note n="0710021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＋（寶）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來【大】，來寶【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710021"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">來寶</rdg></app>塔。
<lb n="0710b29" ed="T"/>一切如<note n="0710022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＋（無量）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來【大】，來無量【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710022"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">來無量</rdg></app>俱胝<note n="0710023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔如胡麻〕ィ－【乙】</note><note n="0710023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如胡麻【大】，〔－〕【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710023"><lem wit="【大】">如胡麻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>心陀羅<note n="0710024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尼＋（密）【乙】</note><note n="0710024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尼【大】，尼密【乙】</note><app n="0710024"><lem wit="【大】">尼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">尼密</rdg></app>印法要。
<pb n="0710c" xml:id="T19.1022A.0710c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0710c01" ed="T"/>今在其中。金剛手有此法要在是中故。<note n="0710025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是〕－【三】【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0710025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0710025"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>塔
<lb n="0710c02" ed="T"/><note n="0710026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＋（變）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】，即變【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710026"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">即變</rdg></app>為如胡<note n="0710027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">麻＋（子）ィ【乙】＊</note><note n="0710027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麻【大】＊，麻子【校異-乙】＊</note><app n="0710027"><lem wit="【大】">麻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">麻子</rdg></app>俱胝百千如來之身。亦<app type="star" corresp="#0710025"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如
<lb n="0710c03" ed="T"/>胡<app type="star" corresp="#0710027"><lem wit="【大】">麻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">麻子</rdg></app>百千俱胝如來全身舍<note n="0710028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＋（之）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0710028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利【大】，利之【校異-乙】</note><app n="0710028"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">利之</rdg></app>聚。乃至八
<lb n="0710c04" ed="T"/>萬四千法蘊亦住其中。即<app type="star" corresp="#0710025"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>九十九百千俱
<lb n="0710c05" ed="T"/>胝如來頂相在其中。是塔一切如來之所授
<lb n="0710c06" ed="T"/>記。若是塔所在之處。有大功勳具大威德能
<lb n="0710c07" ed="T"/>滿一切吉慶。爾時大眾聞佛是說。遠塵離垢
<lb n="0710c08" ed="T"/><note n="0710029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">及隨＝斷諸【乙】</note><note n="0710029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及隨【大】，斷諸【乙】</note><app n="0710029"><lem wit="【大】">及隨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">斷諸</rdg></app>煩惱。得法眼淨。其中即有得須陀洹果
<lb n="0710c09" ed="T"/>者。得斯陀含果者。得阿那含果者。得阿羅漢
<lb n="0710c10" ed="T"/>果者。或有得辟支佛道者。或有入菩薩位者。
<lb n="0710c11" ed="T"/>或有得阿<note n="0710030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鞞＝毘【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0710030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鞞【大】，毘【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0710030"><lem wit="【大】">鞞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">毘</rdg></app>跋致者。或有得菩提授記者。或
<lb n="0710c12" ed="T"/>有得初地二地乃至十地者。或有滿足六波
<lb n="0710c13" ed="T"/>羅蜜者。其婆羅門遠塵離垢得五神通。爾時
<lb n="0710c14" ed="T"/>金剛手菩薩見此奇特希有之事白佛言。世
<lb n="0710c15" ed="T"/>尊甚奇特希有。但聞此事尚獲如是殊勝功
<lb n="0710c16" ed="T"/>德。何況於此法要。種<note n="0710031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">殖＝植【三】【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0710031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殖【大】＊，植【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0710031"><lem wit="【大】">殖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">植</rdg></app>善根獲大福聚。佛
<lb n="0710c17" ed="T"/>言。諦聽金剛<note n="0710032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">手＋（菩薩）【甲】</note><note n="0710032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手【大】，手菩薩【甲】</note><app n="0710032"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">手菩薩</rdg></app>。若有善男子善女人比丘比
<lb n="0710c18" ed="T"/>丘尼優婆塞優婆夷。書寫此經典者。即為書
<lb n="0710c19" ed="T"/>寫彼九十九百千俱胝<note n="0710033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔如胡麻〕－【甲】＊</note><note n="0710033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如胡麻【大】＊，〔－〕【甲】＊</note><app n="0710033"><lem wit="【大】">如胡麻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如來所說經
<lb n="0710c20" ed="T"/>典。即於彼九十九百千俱胝<app type="star" corresp="#0710033"><lem wit="【大】">如胡麻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如來。種
<lb n="0710c21" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0710031"><lem wit="【大】">殖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">植</rdg></app>善根。即為彼等如來護念攝受。若人讀
<lb n="0710c22" ed="T"/>誦。即為讀誦過去一切諸佛所說經典。若受
<lb n="0710c23" ed="T"/>持此經。即彼<note n="0710034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔十方〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0710034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十方【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0710034"><lem wit="【大】">十方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>九十九百千俱胝<app type="star" corresp="#0710033"><lem wit="【大】">如胡
<lb n="0710c24" ed="T"/>麻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如來應正等覺。彼一<note n="0710035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">切＝一【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0710035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">切【大】，一【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0710035"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">一</rdg></app>如來一一方所。遙
<lb n="0710c25" ed="T"/>加攝護晝夜現身。若人供養此經。以<note n="0710036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">花香＝香花【三】【甲】</note><note n="0710036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">花香【大】，香花【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0710036"><lem wit="【大】">花香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">香花</rdg></app>塗
<pb n="0711a" xml:id="T19.1022A.0711a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0711a01" ed="T"/>香花鬘衣服嚴具而供養者。即於彼十方九
<lb n="0711a02" ed="T"/>十九百千俱胝如來之前。成天<note n="0711001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔妙〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711001"><lem wit="【大】">妙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>花妙香衣
<lb n="0711a03" ed="T"/>服嚴具。七寶所成積如須彌。而為供養。種<app type="star" corresp="#0710031"><lem wit="【大】">殖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">植</rdg></app>
<lb n="0711a04" ed="T"/>善根亦復如是。爾時天龍八部人非人等。見
<lb n="0711a05" ed="T"/>聞是已各懷希奇。互相謂言。奇哉威德。是朽
<lb n="0711a06" ed="T"/>土聚以如來神力所加持故。有是神變。時金
<lb n="0711a07" ed="T"/>剛手白佛言。世尊何因緣故。是七寶塔現為
<lb n="0711a08" ed="T"/>土聚。佛告金剛手。此非土聚乃<app type="star" corresp="#0710025"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七寶所成
<lb n="0711a09" ed="T"/>大寶塔耳。復次金剛手由諸眾生業果故隱。
<lb n="0711a10" ed="T"/>非如來全身而可毀壞。豈有如來金剛藏身
<lb n="0711a11" ed="T"/>而可壞也。但以眾生業果因緣。示現隱耳。復
<lb n="0711a12" ed="T"/>次金剛手。後世末法逼迫<note n="0711002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（爾）＋時【三】，（之）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0711002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，爾時【宋】【元】【明】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->之時【校異-乙】</note><app n="0711002"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">爾時</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">之時</rdg></app>。多有眾生習行
<lb n="0711a13" ed="T"/>非法。應墮地獄。不求佛法僧不種<app type="star" corresp="#0710031"><lem wit="【大】">殖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">植</rdg></app>善根。
<lb n="0711a14" ed="T"/>為是因緣妙法當隱。唯除此塔。以一切如來
<lb n="0711a15" ed="T"/>神力所持<note n="0711003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔故〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711003"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。以是事故我今流淚。彼諸如來
<lb n="0711a16" ed="T"/>亦以是事悉皆流淚。爾時金剛手菩薩白佛
<lb n="0711a17" ed="T"/>言。世尊若有人書寫此經安置塔中獲幾所
<lb n="0711a18" ed="T"/>福。佛告金剛手。<note n="0711004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若＋（有）【甲】</note><note n="0711004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，若有【甲】</note><app n="0711004"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">若有</rdg></app>人書寫此經置塔中者。
<lb n="0711a19" ed="T"/>是塔即為一切如來金剛藏窣堵波。亦為一
<lb n="0711a20" ed="T"/>切如來陀羅尼心祕密加持窣堵波。即為九
<lb n="0711a21" ed="T"/>十九百千俱胝<app type="star" corresp="#0710033"><lem wit="【大】">如胡麻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>如來窣堵波。亦為一
<lb n="0711a22" ed="T"/>切如來佛頂佛眼窣堵波。即為一切如來神
<lb n="0711a23" ed="T"/>力所護。若於佛形像中安置。及於一切窣
<lb n="0711a24" ed="T"/>堵波中。安置此經者。其像即為七寶所成。其
<lb n="0711a25" ed="T"/>窣堵波亦為七寶傘蓋。珠網露<note n="0711005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">槃＝盤ィ【乙】</note><note n="0711005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">槃【大】，盤【校異-乙】</note><app n="0711005"><lem wit="【大】">槃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">盤</rdg></app>交結德字
<lb n="0711a26" ed="T"/>鈴鐸純為七寶。一切如來於此法要加其威
<lb n="0711a27" ed="T"/>力。以誠實言本誓加持。若有有情能於此塔
<lb n="0711a28" ed="T"/>種<app type="star" corresp="#0710031"><lem wit="【大】">殖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">植</rdg></app>善根。必定於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提
<lb n="0711a29" ed="T"/><note n="0711006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔得〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711006"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不退轉。乃至應墮阿鼻地<note n="0711007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">獄＋（者）【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獄【大】，獄者【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711007"><lem wit="【大】">獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">獄者</rdg></app>若於此塔
<pb n="0711b" xml:id="T19.1022A.0711b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0711b01" ed="T"/>一禮拜一圍遶必得解脫。皆得不退轉於阿
<lb n="0711b02" ed="T"/>耨多羅三藐三菩提。塔及形像所在之處。一
<lb n="0711b03" ed="T"/>切如來神力所護。其處不為惡風雷雹霹靂
<lb n="0711b04" ed="T"/>所害。又復不為毒蛇毒蟲毒獸所傷。不為惡
<lb n="0711b05" ed="T"/>星怪鳥鸚鵡<note n="0711008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鴝＝鸜【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鴝【大】，鸜【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711008"><lem wit="【大】">鴝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">鸜</rdg></app>鵒蟲鼠虎狼蜂蠆之所傷害。
<lb n="0711b06" ed="T"/>亦無<note n="0711009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">夜＝藥【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜【大】，藥【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711009"><lem wit="【大】">夜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">藥</rdg></app>叉羅剎部多比舍遮癲癎之怖。亦不
<lb n="0711b07" ed="T"/>為一切寒熱諸病癧瘻癰毒瘡癬疥癩所染。
<lb n="0711b08" ed="T"/>若人暫見是塔一切皆除。其處亦無人馬牛
<lb n="0711b09" ed="T"/>疫童子童女疫。亦不為非命所夭。亦不為刀
<lb n="0711b10" ed="T"/>杖水火所傷。亦不為他敵所侵。飢饉所逼。厭
<lb n="0711b11" ed="T"/>魅呪<note n="0711010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">詛＝禱【三】【乙】</note><note n="0711010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">詛【大】，禱【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0711010"><lem wit="【大】">詛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">禱</rdg></app>不能得<note n="0711011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔便〕－【甲】</note><note n="0711011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0711011"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。四大天王與諸眷屬。晝
<lb n="0711b12" ed="T"/>夜衛<note n="0711012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔護〕－【甲】</note><note n="0711012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">護【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0711012"><lem wit="【大】">護</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。二十八部大藥叉將。及日月<note n="0711013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𧘂暈＝憧雲【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𧘂暈【大】，憧雲【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711013"><lem wit="【大】">𧘂暈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">憧雲</rdg></app>
<lb n="0711b13" ed="T"/>彗星晝夜護持。一切龍王加其精氣順時降
<lb n="0711b14" ed="T"/>雨。一切諸天與忉利天三時下來。亦為供養
<lb n="0711b15" ed="T"/>禮拜塔故。一切諸仙三時來集讚詠旋遶。釋
<lb n="0711b16" ed="T"/>提桓因與諸天女。晝夜三時來下供養。其處
<lb n="0711b17" ed="T"/>即為一切如來護念加持。若人作塔或土石
<lb n="0711b18" ed="T"/>木金銀赤銅。書此法要安置其中。纔安置已
<lb n="0711b19" ed="T"/>其塔即為七寶所成。上下階陛露<note n="0711014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">槃＝盤【甲】</note><note n="0711014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">槃【大】，盤【甲】</note><app n="0711014"><lem wit="【大】">槃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">盤</rdg></app>傘蓋鈴
<lb n="0711b20" ed="T"/>鐸網綴純為七寶。其塔四方如來形<note n="0711015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">像＝相【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">像【大】，相【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711015"><lem wit="【大】">像</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">相</rdg></app><note n="0711016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔亦復…持〕十三字ィ－【乙】</note><note n="0711016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（亦復…持）十三字【大】，〔－〕【校異-乙】</note><app cb:word-count="13" n="0711016"><lem wit="【大】">亦
<lb n="0711b21" ed="T"/>復如是。則一切如來神力所持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。其七寶塔<note n="0711017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕ィ－【乙】</note><note n="0711017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，〔－〕【校異-乙】</note><app n="0711017"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0711b22" ed="T"/>全身舍<note n="0711018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＋（之妙寶）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0711018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利【大】，利之妙寶【校異-乙】</note><app n="0711018"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">利之妙寶</rdg></app>藏。高至阿迦尼吒天<note n="0711019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宮＋（之中）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0711019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">宮【大】，宮之中【校異-乙】</note><app n="0711019"><lem wit="【大】">宮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">宮之中</rdg></app>。一切諸
<lb n="0711b23" ed="T"/>天守衛供養。金剛手白佛言。世尊何因緣故
<lb n="0711b24" ed="T"/>此法。如是殊勝功德。</p>
<lb n="0711b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0711b2501">佛告金剛手。以此寶篋陀羅尼威神力故。金
<lb n="0711b26" ed="T"/>剛手言。<app type="star" corresp="#0710007"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">惟</rdg></app>願如來。哀愍我等說是陀羅尼。
<lb n="0711b27" ed="T"/>佛言。諦聽金剛手。此是<note n="0711020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一切如來〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0711020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一切如來【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0711020"><lem wit="【大】">一切如來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>未來現在
<lb n="0711b28" ed="T"/>及已般涅槃者全身舍利。皆在寶<note n="0711021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">篋＋（印）ィ【乙】</note><note n="0711021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">篋【大】，篋印【校異-乙】</note><app n="0711021"><lem wit="【大】">篋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark">篋印</rdg></app>陀羅尼
<lb n="0711b29" ed="T"/>中。是諸如來所有三身亦在是中。爾時世尊
<pb n="0711c" xml:id="T19.1022A.0711c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0711c01" ed="T"/>即說陀羅尼曰。</p>
